00:36:29.380 --> 00:36:30.930
[Donante Park Gi Yeong]

00:37:24.460 --> 00:37:28.440
El donante del corazón de Cha Yeong Woon, Park Gi Yeong.

00:37:30.450 --> 00:37:34.530
No podía creerlo. Pero...

00:37:34.530 --> 00:37:37.200
